edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.templates

Class HWP

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.templates.HWP

  • public class HWP
extends Object
    Define hardware available on cRIO platform for FRC 2009, FRC 2010, FRC 2011, FRC2012 This is a tedious, but useful one-time-per-season task. Only edit this section to add resources or correct errors or when the control system changes The I/O available on the platform is arranged by I/O type in order to help track resource usage if I/O is scarce This serves as documentation and is useful to co-ordinate with other project members (electrical and mechanical)
    Author:
    MentorPete
